{
  "name": "SortField",
  "summary": "<p>开发人员可以使用 <strong>BeforeSort</strong> 事件重写 ET 的默认行为，将自己的排序算法写入应用程序中。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例遍历活动工作表的排序字段，将偶数位的排序字段设置为升序排序。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sortfields = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sort</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SortFields</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= sortfields.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (i % <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span> == <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>) {\n            sortfields.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Order</span> = xlDescending\n        }\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在活动工作表新建排序字段，并显示该排序字段是否按字体颜色对数据进行升序排序。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sortfield = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sort</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SortFields</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A3&quot;</span>), xlSortOnFontColor, xlAscending)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (sortfield.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SortOn</span> == xlSortOnFontColor &amp;&amp; sortfield.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Order</span> == xlAscending) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;排序字段按字体颜色对数据进行升序排序&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;排序字段未按字体颜色和升序进行排序&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p><strong>SortField</strong> 对象包含 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Worksheet/Worksheet .htm#Worksheet.Worksheet\">Worksheet</a></strong>、<strong>Lists</strong> 和 <strong>AutoFilter</strong> 对象的所有排序信息。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "<p>您可以将此属性与 OLE 自动化对象一起使用以返回该对象的应用程序。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>如果不与对象识别符一起使用，则此属性返回代表 ET 应用程序的 **<a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Application/Application .htm#Application.Application\">Application</a>**对象。如果与对象识别符一起使用，则此属性返回代表指定对象的创建者的 **<a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Application/Application .htm#Application.Application\">Application</a>**对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "XlCreator",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "CustomOrder",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>指定对字段进行排序的自定义次序。可读/写 <strong>Variant</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在活动工作表设置自定义排序。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sort</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SortFields</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">CustomOrder</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A,B,C,D,E,F,G,H&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在第一张工作表创建新的排序字段，并显示第一张工作表的自定义排序。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sort</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SortFields</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A20&quot;</span>), xlSortOnValues, xlAscending, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;alpha,bravo,charlie,delta&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sort</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SortFields</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">CustomOrder</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "DataOption",
      "summary": "<p>**<a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlSortDataOption 枚举.html\">xlSortDataOption</a>**可以是 **<a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlSortDataOption 枚举.html\">xlSortNormal</a>**或 <strong><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlSortDataOption 枚举.html\">xlSortTextAsNumbers</a></strong>。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>指定<strong>SortField</strong> 对象所指定的区域中的文本排序方式。可读/写 <a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlSortDataOption 枚举.html\"><strong>XlSortDataOption</strong></a>类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表将文本作为数字型数据进行排序。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sort</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SortFields</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataOption</span> = xlSortTextAsNumbers\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断第一张工作表的文本排序方式。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sort = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sort</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SortFields</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (sort.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataOption</span> == xlSortNormal) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;分别对数字和文本数据进行排序&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;将文本作为数字型数据进行排序&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "XlSortDataOption",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Key",
      "summary": "<p>关键字可以是区域名称（字符串）或 <strong>Range</strong> 对象。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>指定排序字段，该字段确定要排序的值。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在第一张工作表创建新的排序字段，并显示第一张工作表排序字段的键值地址。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sort</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SortFields</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A20&quot;</span>), xlSortOnValues)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sort</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SortFields</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Key</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Address</span>())\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在活动工作表创建两个新的排序字段，并显示所有排序字段的键值地址。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sort = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sort</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SortFields</span>\n    sort.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A20&quot;</span>))\n    sort.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1&quot;</span>), xlSortOnValues)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= sort.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(sort.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Key</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Address</span>())\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Range",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Order",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>确定关键字所指定的值的排序次序。可读/写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在活动工作表创建新的排序字段，并设置该排序字段的排序次序为降序。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sortfields = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sort</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SortFields</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A4&quot;</span>))\n    sortfields.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Order</span> = xlDescending\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在第一张工作表创建新的排序字段，并显示该排序字段的排序次序是否为升序。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Activate</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sortfield = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sort</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SortFields</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>), xlSortOnValues, xlAscending)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(sortfield.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Order</span> == xlAscending)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "XlSortOrder",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Parent",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定对象的父对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Priority",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>指定排序字段的优先级。可读/写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在第一张工作表创建新的排序字段，并显示该排序字段是否为最主要的排序字段。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sortfield = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sort</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SortFields</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:B4&quot;</span>))\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(sortfield.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Priority</span> == <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断如果活动工作表 SortField 对象的数量大于2，则将活动工作表第三个排序字段设置为次要的排序字段。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sortfields = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sort</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SortFields</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (sortfields.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span> &gt; <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>) {\n        sortfields.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Priority</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "SortOn",
      "summary": "<div id=\"vstable\" style=\"font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th>XlSortOn 可以是下列 <strong>XlSortOn</strong> 常量之一：</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>SortOnCellColor</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>SortOnFontColor</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>SortOnIcon</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>SortOnValues</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置要排序的单元格属性。可读/写 **<a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlSortOn 枚举.html\">XlSortOn</a>**类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在第一张工作表新建排序字段，并显示该排序字段是否按字体颜色对数据进行排序。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sortfield = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sort</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SortFields</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:B10&quot;</span>), xlSortOnFontColor)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(sortfield.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SortOn</span> == xlSortOnFontColor)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在活动工作表新建排序字段，并设置该排序字段根据单元格颜色进行排序。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sortfield = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sort</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SortFields</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:B10&quot;</span>))\n    sortfield.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SortON</span> = xlSortOnCellColor\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "XlSortOn",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "SortOnValue",
      "summary": "<p><strong>SortOnValue</strong> 可与值、单元格颜色、字体颜色和单元格图标一起使用。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回指定 <strong>SortField</strong> 对象执行排序的值。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例按字体颜色对 Sheet1 上的 B 列中的数据进行升序排序。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sort</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SortFields</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Clear</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sort</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SortFields</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1:B25&quot;</span>), xlSortOnFontColor, xlAscending, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>, xlSortNormal).<span class=\"hljs-property\">SortOnValue</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sort = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sort</span>\n    sort.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SetRange</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:B25&quot;</span>))\n    sort.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Header</span> = xlGuess\n    sort.<span class=\"hljs-property\">MatchCase</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n    sort.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Orientation</span> = xlTopToBottom\n    sort.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SortMethod</span> = xlPinYin\n    sort.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Apply</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在活动工作表新建排序字段，并设置该字段分别按照单元格颜色等方式对数据进行排序。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sortfield = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sort</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SortFields</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C5&quot;</span>), xlSortOnCellColor)\n    sortfield.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SortOnValue</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//设置该字段按字体颜色对数据进行排序</span>\n    sortfield.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sorton</span> = xlSortOnFontColor\n    sortfield.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SortOnValue</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//设置该字段按图标对数据进行排序</span>\n    sortfield.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sorton</span> = xlSortOnIcon\n    sortfield.<span class=\"hljs-property\">SortOnValue</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n    sortfield.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SetIcon</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">IconSets</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>))\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
