ield.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SetIcon</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">IconSets</span>(xl3Signs).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>))\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
